						<summary>

						<p>Ruined Īśvara temple, north wall, left of entrance.</p>						

						<p><hi rend="bold">••• •••• Śaka 1202 (current) Pra[māthi] MIṉa, śu. 2, Monday, Aśvati = 1280 A.D., March 4, f.d.n. 23.</hi><note n="147-1">Cf. <hi rend="italic">A.R.Ep.,</hi> 1914, p. 73.</note></p>						

						<p>Records the gift of 12 <hi rend="italic">māḍai</hi> for a perpetual lamp for God Pāpanāśamuḍaiya-nāyaṉār by Paṇḍitaṉ Pākkiḻāṉ Gaṇḍarādittaṉ Aruḷāḷaperumāḷ. The endowment was taken over by <hi rend="italic">sthānapatigaḷ.</hi></p>						

						</summary>
